    com.i2group.apollo.alertfeedservice.IAlertFeedService.createAlertFeed(String, String, String, ItemIdentifier, List<SecurityAccessPermission>, List<SecurityGrantPermission>, String, List<String>, List<AlertDeliveryMechanism>)

    Use IAdminService.setSchema(Schema) and IAdminService.setRepositoryName(String) instead.

    com.i2group.disco.audit.IRecordInfo.getId()
    com.i2group.apollo.infoservice.IInfoService.getSecurityDimensionsForCurrentUser()
    Use the SecuritySchema to determine what SecurityDimensions are available.
    com.i2group.apollo.infoservice.IInfoService.getSecuritySchemesForCurrentUser()
    This method always returns an empty SecuritySchemeList. Instead, use the SecuritySchema to determine what SecurityTags are available.

    Use IAdminService.setSecuritySchema(SecuritySchema) instead.
